                            <comment id="13645152" author="nehanarkhede" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 02:01:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch shuffles the list of brokers used by both producer and consumer to fetch metadata. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13645736" author="jjkoshy" created="Tue, 30 Apr 2013 17:13:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is worth noting that this is useful even in the presence of a VIP since the consumers don&apos;t currently use a VIP to to look up metadata.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
